---
title: Seared Salmon & Lemon Sauce with Golden Potatoes & Courgette
description: Sometimes, great cooking is a flurry of clever techniques and a dizzying array of ingredients. Other times, it’s the simplicity of just a few things; dill, butter, lemon, potatoes and beautiful salmon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c85a2e8e3f339510a6854a2-ce49374a.jpg
